Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.00,0:00:33.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,很久以前,阿肯人统治整个银河系.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.31,0:00:37.40,Default,,0,0,0,,它们身后满是恐怖和疮痍.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.00,0:00:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,它们那可怕的力量之源...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.19,0:00:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,遗落在乌诺波里斯星球的密室中.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:50.95,Default,,0,0,0,,其中蕴含着神秘的永生之泉.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.79,0:00:56.42,Default,,0,0,0,,密室只能被一把独一无二的钥匙打开...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.46,0:00:58.79,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦被人找到..
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.25,0:01:04.55,Default,,0,0,0,,它将会引导发现者得到永生之泉.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.26,0:01:10.93,Default,,0,0,0,,然而,那把钥匙令所有接触到它的人变得疯狂.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.64,0:01:17.27,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯人最终被击败，他们的力量之源被锁在密室中的时候...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.36,0:01:21.61,Default,,0,0,0,,那把钥匙也被流放到宇宙深处.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.96,0:01:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再也没有出现过...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.61,0:01:27.82,Default,,0,0,0,,直到现在.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.00,0:02:59.42,Default,,0,0,0,,哼!快点投降，你这混蛋！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶!又来了!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.30,0:03:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经等不及拿到那些新设备了.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:11.80,0:03:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,我已经受够了这些便宜货了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒,我好像发现了什么
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.78,0:03:34.95,Default,,0,0,0,,什么东西?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.41,0:03:39.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.27,0:03:57.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,小心点，这可能是四级生化物品
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.48,0:04:00.31,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.90,0:04:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,它在做什么?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.25,0:04:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,真是诡异
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.40,0:04:48.81,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么回事?你还好吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.90,0:04:52.15,Default,,0,0,0,,需要我呼叫紧急救助吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.73,0:04:57.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不要，求求你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.53,0:04:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干什么!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.94,0:05:30.86,Default,,0,0,0,,守护者已经显灵!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.74,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙已经被发现了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.25,0:05:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,奥丁，告诉我们
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.78,0:05:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,巨大的黑暗是否即将到来?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.50,0:05:39.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,是的，正如古书说记载的那样
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.80,0:05:43.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黑暗即将回归
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.50,0:05:47.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,邪恶即将到来
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.20,0:05:50.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我们必须做好准备守护密室
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.48,0:06:14.15,Default,,0,0,0,,桑达斯, 3号区域!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.44,0:06:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我们还在等待当地核心的初步分析结果.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.40,0:06:19.59,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？他们下去多久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.17,0:06:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,超过12个小时.他们肯定快疯了.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.33,0:06:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,真奇怪. 系统没问他,但一直没有回复. 怪事.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.88,0:06:33.30,Default,,0,0,0,,送几个人下去.我要弄清楚到底发生什么事情.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.00,0:06:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要一艘大船去些地方.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.59,0:06:38.72,Default,,0,0,0,,见鬼，你知道你在做什么吗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.76,0:06:40.47,Default,,0,0,0,,保安，到舰桥来
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.15,0:06:51.98,Default,,0,0,0,,还有其他蠢问题吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.69,0:06:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,胖子. 你的名字和职务
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.41,0:07:03.58,Default,,0,0,0,,- 兰伯特,长官. 导航员.\N- 开船.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.79,0:07:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,吉尔曼 St. 吉尔曼.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.25,0:07:10.42,Default,,0,0,0,,若我想知道你的名字, 呆瓜,我会问你的.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.58,0:07:12.25,Default,,0,0,0,,接管引擎.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.54,0:07:15.55,Default,,0,0,0,,导航定位至 BR-549,区域7.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.38,0:07:18.05,Default,,0,0,0,,另外，来人把这些垃圾弄走
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.76,0:07:25.01,Default,,0,0,0,,另外...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你有20秒时间带我们离开这里
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.05,0:11:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Hi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.17,0:11:28.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你还在这里干啥?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.01,0:11:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道. 我一会就会上学迟到.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.80,0:11:33.05,Default,,0,0,0,,爸爸在哪儿?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.14,0:11:36.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他在议会，我以为你也应该去的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.57,0:11:37.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦，糟糕！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.78,0:11:49.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你相信那些所谓的不朽的妄言吗?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.24,0:11:58.66,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看.一把愚蠢的钥匙?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.58,0:12:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个骗子,瞧着吧.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.67,0:12:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，这家伙自从那天开始就变得越来越诡异了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.33,0:12:07.30,Default,,0,0,0,,想想看再来10年? 见鬼, 甚至100年.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.67,0:12:10.17,Default,,0,0,0,,你说到点子上了.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.30,0:12:14.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我讨厌这鬼地方，特别是翻遍这个丑陋的地方\NI am getting sick of it.Going all over the bloody place.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.76,0:12:17.01,Default,,0,0,0,,寻找一个荒谬的谎言\NLooking for a stupid compound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.23,0:12:23.27,Default,,0,0,0,,-你找到了什么东西？-一个FAKK2号行星\N- What have you got?  - A FAKK 2 planet, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.19,0:12:27.02,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯，这地方对碳基生命来说意味着死亡\NDeath to all carbon based life forms.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.57,0:12:31.90,Default,,0,0,0,,议会指定的二级杀戮死亡地带\NFederation Assigned Kitogenic Killzone to the second level.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.95,0:12:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,这里是一个死行星\NWhich means it's a dead planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.82,0:12:36.16,Default,,0,0,0,,对它进行扫描\NScan it anyway.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.49,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我不明白\NI don't get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.75,0:12:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这外面有生命存在\NThere's life out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.50,0:12:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这个FAKK2号行星的注册信息肯定过时了\NThe FAKK 2 must have been from an old registry.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.79,0:12:49.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我想要这个地方H2O-471化合物的生物扫描结果\NI want a bio-scan for compound H2O-471.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.39,0:13:00.06,Default,,0,0,0,,他们的生态系统里一定有什么线索\NThere are small traces in their systems.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.56,0:13:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,到处都有不朽的线索\NYeah. Immortality all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.90,0:13:05.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你！\NYou!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.48,0:13:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,记着你的小命还不是不朽的\NJust remember you're not immortal yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.40,0:13:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这地方叫什么？\NWhat's this place called?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.41,0:13:16.62,Default,,0,0,0,,伊甸，长官\NEden, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.45,0:13:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到天堂\NWelcome to paradise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:31.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的灌溉计划已经初见成效\NAnd our irrigation program is already showing promise.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.42,0:13:36.09,Default,,0,0,0,,上半年农产品的产量增长了5个百分点\NAgro-production is up five percent in the last six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.39,0:13:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的扩张项目也将进入第二阶段\NPhase two of our expansion project...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.93,0:13:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,诺玛区的开发，按照程序将在三周后开始\Nthe development of the Noma Valley,will begin in three weeks as scheduled.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.81,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都很顺利，先生门女士们，我们的未来一片光明\NThings look good, ladies and gentlemen.Our future is bright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.66,0:14:04.42,Default,,0,0,0,,-你去帮助凯瑞，我去打开防卫系统。\N- Help Kerrie. I'll get our air defences up! 
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.42,0:14:04.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-小心点，我会去那找你。\N - Be careful! I'll see you up there!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.17,0:14:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,快，这边走！\NQuickly. This way!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.00,0:14:49.17,Default,,0,0,0,,凯瑞！\NKerrie!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.34,0:17:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉\NJulie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.05,0:17:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,父亲！\NFather!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.59,0:17:49.76,Default,,0,0,0,,看来我们的家伙有点好战\NLooks like the boys got a little trigger-happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.43,0:17:53.81,Default,,0,0,0,,在做煎蛋卷时，先得打碎几个鸡蛋\NWhen making an omelette,one breaks a few eggs.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.23,0:18:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这，我来帮你\NHere, let me help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.20,0:18:11.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,他们在攻击\NThey attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.99,0:18:13.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,-你还好吗？-我们没希望了\N- You okay? - We never had a chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.83,0:18:18.54,Default,,0,0,0,,嘿，看看这个！一个女人！\NHey, look at this! A live one!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,离她远点！\NLeave her alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.97,0:18:30.97,Default,,0,0,0,,滚开！离我远点！\NGet off of me! Let me go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.35,0:18:40.94,Default,,0,0,0,,活泼又性感\NFeisty and sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:43.73,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计们小心点，这家伙是战利品\NCareful boys, this one's a keeper.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.57,0:18:47.53,Default,,0,0,0,,-把他们铐起来！-是，长官！\N- Pack 'em up!- Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.95,0:18:50.49,Default,,0,0,0,,快点，伙计们！我们要离开了！\NSplitsville, boys! We're moving out!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.08,0:19:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,等等我！\NWait for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.88,0:19:05.63,Default,,0,0,0,,可怜的小家伙，你只能靠你自己了\NLover-boy, you're on your own.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.92,0:19:08.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能就这样扔下我！\NYou can't just leave me here like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.59,0:19:11.39,Default,,0,0,0,,等会\NWait a minute, man...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.27,0:19:20.35,Default,,0,0,0,,就像他说的，这是个死行星\NLike the sign says, a dead planet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.47,0:19:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,这不会伤到你，只是一个DNA测试\NThis won't hurt. It's just a DNA test.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.43,0:19:57.31,Default,,0,0,0,,好结果总是来得晚\NThe good stuff comes later.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.02,0:20:01.90,Default,,0,0,0,,博士，从其他人开始\NStart with the others, Doc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:06.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-这个人非常独特  -当然\N- This one's special.- But of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.32,0:20:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我需要的东西就在你们体内\NWhat I need is in your system.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.95,0:20:12.74,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不足以另你们不朽\NNot enough to make you immortal...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.78,0:20:18.04,Default,,0,0,0,,但是足以令你们保持美丽和健康，特别是你\Nbut it probably keeps your people beautiful and healthy. Especially you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.75,0:20:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,我会把你留到最后\NI'll save you for last.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,假如你运气好的话，亲爱的，最好放聪明一点\NAnd if you're lucky, my dear,and play your cards right...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.13,0:20:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会待在一起很长时间\Nwe'll spend a lot of quality time together.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.89,0:20:41.18,Default,,0,0,0,,完美，我知道你不会令我失望的\NPerfect. I knew you wouldn't disappoint me.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.23,0:20:43.52,Default,,0,0,0,,把她清理干净\NClean her up!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.94,0:20:46.48,Default,,0,0,0,,相信不用我强调\NAnd I don't have to remind your kind...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.19,0:20:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,她是我的\Nshe's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.42,0:22:38.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该成为一个厨师的\NI should have been a cook!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.47,0:22:41.51,Default,,0,0,0,,尝尝这个!\NTry this for an appetiser!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.55,0:22:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我没做任何坏事  -你是他们一伙的\N- I didn't do anything! I swear! - You're one of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.06,0:22:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不是的，我的意思是，我曾是，但是我逃走了！我也没有杀掉任何人！\NNo! I mean, I was, but I ran away!I didn't kill anybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.56,0:22:49.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这到底是谁干的？\NWho did this?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.98,0:22:52.61,Default,,0,0,0,,他抢了我们的船然后逼我们来这儿\NHe took over our ship and forced us to come here!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.65,0:22:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁 ？ -他的名字叫泰勒！\N- Who? - His name's Tyler!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.78,0:22:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他要袭击我们？\NWhy did he attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.11,0:22:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,他是个疯子！他想得到永生!\NHe's nuts!He thinks he's going to live forever!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.03,0:23:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,他要去哪里？你有一秒时间回答\NWhere did he go? You've got one second.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:04.70,Default,,0,0,0,,1\NOne....
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.08,0:23:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,等等！我会带你去找到他\NWait! I'll take you to him!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.12,0:23:10.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-哪儿？-我们达成协议了吗？\N- Where?- Do we have a deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.17,0:23:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,-修好这艘飞船需要多久？-2小时，最多！我马上就要完工了\N- How long to fix this Spacehawk?- Two hours, max! I'm almost there.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.72,0:23:24.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你把你的扳手丢了，难道你不应该去捡起来吗？\NYou dropped your wrench.Aren't you going to pick it up?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.39,0:23:26.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.56,0:23:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,我又做了什么吗？\NWhat did I do?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.79,0:23:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个天才\NI am a genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.96,0:23:57.46,Default,,0,0,0,,博士，这个最好奏效\NDoc, this had better work.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:08.35,0:24:10.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我喜欢这种淡淡的柠檬味\NI like the hint of lemon.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:13.02,Default,,0,0,0,,真令人开心\NI'm so glad.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.11,0:24:16.32,Default,,0,0,0,,是的\NYes!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.08,0:24:27.58,Default,,0,0,0,,然后，我们要去哪儿？\NSo, where are we going?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:29.41,0:24:32.00,Default,,0,0,0,,他说过他要去一个穿梭泊口\NHe said he needed to get to a jump port.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.17,0:24:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,电脑，设定坐标去最近的宇宙港口\NComputer, set co-ordinates for the closest spaceport...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:35.04,0:24:37.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那种能容纳C级太空船的\Nthat can handle a class C vessel.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:37.80,0:24:41.97,Default,,0,0,0,,搜索，确认，Neo Calcutta，设定航线\NSearching. Confirmed.Neo Calcutta. Course set.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.22,0:24:44.34,Default,,0,0,0,,ETA 93.7 个小时.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.28,0:25:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,那个，你的名字叫什么\NSo, what's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:02.40,0:25:05.62,Default,,0,0,0,,禁止说话，禁止乱碰，你最好连呼吸都不要···\NDon't talk, don't touch,don't even breathe...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:05.70,0:25:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,否则我会杀了 你，明白了吗？-我明白了\Nor I kill you. Got it?- I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.55,0:26:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,请求对接\NRequest incoming docking co-ordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.39,0:26:09.51,Default,,0,0,0,,请保持航向\NPlease continue holding pattern.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:09.80,0:26:15.73,Default,,0,0,0,,请停泊到ANUS-6370\NLock in approach at ANUS-6370.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.60,0:26:19.81,Default,,0,0,0,,-确认 -请表明你的来意\N- Confirmed.- State the purpose of your visit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:19.98,0:26:22.44,Default,,0,0,0,,-复仇 -处理中\N- Revenge.- Processing.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:23.03,0:26:25.82,Default,,0,0,0,,输入无效，请重新提交\NInvalid entry. Resubmit.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.78,0:26:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,-处理家事 -确认\N- Family business.- Confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:29.49,0:26:31.28,Default,,0,0,0,,准许停留48小时\NForty-eight hour access.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:31.74,0:26:36.91,Default,,0,0,0,,签证号 URFUKD-881\NVisa file number URFUKD-881.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.54,0:26:39.54,Default,,0,0,0,,请提交身份证明\NPlease submit identity.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.34,0:26:44.51,Default,,0,0,0,,FAKK 2行星\NFAKK 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:44.63,0:26:47.18,Default,,0,0,0,,确认，解除对接\NConfirmed. Cleared for docking.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.63,0:27:25.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这地方吗？\NYou like this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:26.01,0:27:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去有很多你的同类\NLooks like a lot of your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:29.63,0:27:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,在一起待在战斗机4天后，结果还是只得到冷漠对待···\NAfter four days stuck in a Spacehawk,getting the cold shoulder...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:33.39,0:27:36.43,Default,,0,0,0,,并没有那么糟糕，我们在这里能找到很多乐子\Nit's not so bad.We could have a lot of fun here.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:36.56,0:27:38.73,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么人，可怜虫吗？\NWhat are you, socially deprived?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:38.77,0:27:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是可怜虫，当然，或许有一点点是\NI'm not socially deprived.Well, maybe a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.81,0:27:48.36,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下，你在看什么？你在打呼噜\NSit down! What are you looking at?You snore!
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.86,0:27:51.49,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远点！给我闭嘴！\NGet outta my face! Shut the fuck up!'
Dialogue: 0,0:27:52.70,0:27:55.37,Default,,0,0,0,,相比我来的地方这里简直就是天堂\NThis is heaven compared to where I come from.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.12,0:27:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴！\NShut the fuck up.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.88,0:28:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你确定泰勒在找穿梭泊口？还有他到底要去哪儿？\NAre you sure this guy Tyler is lookingfor a jump port? And to where?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.76,0:28:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在卖的是高级货色，由真正的硅橡胶构成\NWe're talking high-grade,silicone-rubber flesh here.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.85,0:28:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,还有PVC骨架，塑料插座能保证满足你的需要\NAnd a PVC skeleton with plastic ball and socket joints for optimum movement.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.10,0:28:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,你能为她设定七种发型\NYou can customise her with a choice of seven synthetic hair dyes.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.52,0:28:30.74,Default,,0,0,0,,并且还有四档速可以选择\NAnd optional entry ports with four speeds of suction!
Dialogue: 0,0:28:32.20,0:28:33.74,Default,,0,0,0,,她很可爱，不是吗？\NLoveable, isn't she?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:35.28,0:28:36.83,Default,,0,0,0,,再看看这个\NCheck this out.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.87,0:28:40.83,Default,,0,0,0,,她装载了最新的微型传感器架构技术\NShe's loaded with the latest micro-sensor orgasmatronic technology...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:41.00,0:28:43.17,Default,,0,0,0,,还有可扩展的语言库\Nand an expandable vocabulary...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.21,0:28:46.67,Default,,0,0,0,,超过200句脏话\Nof over 200 dirty words.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.71,0:28:49.92,Default,,0,0,0,,测试结果显示她比真人还要好\NTest results indicate she's better than the real thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:50.34,0:28:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,来，维纳斯，让大家看看你的本事\NGo on, Venus.Show the gentleman what you got.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:56.68,0:28:59.52,Default,,0,0,0,,请选择性爱模式\NPlease select your sexual preference.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.64,0:29:03.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Vaginal. Anal. Oral. Other.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.48,0:29:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,只卖2000块\NOnly 2,000.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:06.69,0:29:09.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我不确定，2000块···\NI don't know, 2,000....
Dialogue: 0,0:29:09.57,0:29:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,当然，或许你更喜欢其他模式\NUnless, of course,you'd prefer the Fellation Blowfish.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.03,0:29:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,病态，扭曲，低级，无耻的混蛋\NSick, twisted, low-life, scum sucking pig!
Dialogue: 0,0:29:19.08,0:29:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,至少我想有人能陪我说会话\NAt least I'll have someone to talk to.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:22.71,0:29:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啥？\NWhat?
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.87,0:29:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,就是那家伙，那个高个子\NThat's him. The tall one.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.92,0:29:32.13,Default,,0,0,0,,-走 -我在这里等着\N- Let's go.- I'll wait here.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:32.47,0:29:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他会发现我，你根本不知道他的可怕\NBut he'll see me.You don't know what he's like.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:36.51,0:29:37.76,Default,,0,0,0,,胆小鬼\NChicken shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.23,0:30:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,天哪，这真是有趣！\NGod, this is fun!
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.75,0:30:55.46,Default,,0,0,0,,没人能碰这些东西\NNobody touches these...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:57.93,0:30:59.05,Default,,0,0,0,,除了我\Nbut me!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:00.64,0:31:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,毛巾\NBar towel!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.78,0:31:20.95,Default,,0,0,0,,你好，泰勒船长，金属矿产开发商\NHello? Captain Tyler,Metal Mammoth Mining.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:21.07,0:31:22.95,Default,,0,0,0,,给我们拿点喝的\NWe need some drinks!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:27.62,0:31:30.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们得抓紧时间，我们可不想错过传送\NWe should make it fast.We don't want to miss the jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.54,0:31:32.88,Default,,0,0,0,,去他的的传送\NScrew the jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:33.29,0:31:35.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我拥有花不完的时间\NI've got all the time in the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.59,0:31:38.38,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外，有意思的事情来了\NBesides, something just came up.
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.14,0:31:43.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你刚刚碰到你的白马王子\NYou just found the man of your dreams.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:50.33,0:32:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,当你杀掉某人时，亲爱的，确保他已经死透了\NWhen you kill someone, darling,make sure he's dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.83,0:32:56.09,Default,,0,0,0,,什么情况？\NWhat the hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:46.39,0:33:48.39,Default,,0,0,0,,看上去快乐时光结束了\NLooks like happy hour is over.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.22,0:33:52.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-谁来赔这些东西？-这些应该够了\N- Who's gonna pay for all of this? - This ought to take care of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:53.02,0:33:55.23,Default,,0,0,0,,给你，不用找了\NHere. Keep the change.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.77,0:33:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？可恶！\NWhat? Holy shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.40,0:33:59.48,Default,,0,0,0,,炸弹！\NGrenades!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.38,0:34:20.50,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉？\NJulie?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:25.38,0:34:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\NAre you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:30.05,0:34:33.56,Default,,0,0,0,,他死了！但他却死而复生了！\NHe died! And then he was alive again!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.06,0:34:35.43,Default,,0,0,0,,现在你明白啦\NNow you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:36.69,0:34:39.23,Default,,0,0,0,,我一点也不想知道！他到底是怎么做到的？\NI don't know dick! How does he do it?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.27,0:34:41.27,Default,,0,0,0,,他注射了一种奇怪的药\NHe's got this weird potion!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.32,0:34:43.98,Default,,0,0,0,,那把钥匙会指引他到达永生之所\NAnd a key leading him to the Chamber of lmmortality.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:44.03,0:34:46.28,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你之前不告诉我这些？\NWhy didn't you tell me that before?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.36,0:34:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,坐下!离我远点!还有给我闭嘴！\NSit down. Get outta my face!Shut the fuck up!
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.83,0:34:56.75,Default,,0,0,0,,也就是说如果我拿走他的药，他就会死翘翘，是吗？\NSo if I take away his potion,he'll stay dead, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:56.79,0:34:59.83,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你做得足够彻底的话\NIf you can get close enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.80,0:35:04.46,Default,,0,0,0,,那个就是他，是不是？\NThat's him, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.59,0:35:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,可恶，他要离开了\NSon of a bitch, he's getting away!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:07.30,0:35:10.34,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙的暴君还需要什么？\NWhat more could the universe want in a tyrant?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.18,0:35:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,完美的身体，完美的大脑\NPerfect body, perfect mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.52,0:35:18.64,Default,,0,0,0,,-无法抗拒的魅力 -彻彻底底的神经病\N- Irresistible charm.- Perfect psycho!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.69,0:35:23.02,Default,,0,0,0,,神经病？到出来玩游戏的时间了\NPsycho? Time to come out and play.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:23.07,0:35:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,想都别想\NDon't even think about it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.61,0:35:31.91,Default,,0,0,0,,空间跳跃时，总会发生一些事情\NThe hyperspace jump.There's always something.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.33,0:35:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我晚点会弥补你的，甜心\NI'll make it up to you later, sweetheart.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:37.25,0:35:39.92,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧让我离开这，你们这群混蛋\NLet me out of here, you bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.72,0:36:00.19,Default,,0,0,0,,科尔斯特号飞船呼叫跳跃中心，设定航线去乌诺布里斯\NCortez to Jump Control.Set lock-in for Uroboris.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.31,0:36:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,没有历史数据，开始重新设计航线\NNo pre-set lock-in. Set co-ordinates.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.86,0:36:07.57,Default,,0,0,0,,特拉肯星系，第9象限，4013区\NQuadrant 9, sector 4013,in the Terackian system.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.94,0:36:09.78,Default,,0,0,0,,扫描地址\NScanning location.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.57,0:36:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,警告，没有返程传送泊岸\NWarning. No returnjump port.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.78,0:36:15.74,Default,,0,0,0,,请确认\NPlease confirm lock-in.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.33,0:36:17.62,Default,,0,0,0,,确认\NConfirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.54,0:36:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我们会一辈子困在那里\NIt'll take us forever to get back!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.42,0:36:23.92,Default,,0,0,0,,一旦我们到达那里，这都将不再是问题\NThat won't be a problem,once we get there.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:27.38,0:36:29.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不可能成功！这就是一条死路！\NWe'll never make it!This thing's a death trap!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.34,0:36:34.93,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们已经走了这么远了 -这点旅程根本不算什么\N- It's gotten us this far.- This far is nowhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.10,0:36:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,在超空间航行就是在找死\NSpacehawk in hyperspace equals death!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:37.60,0:36:39.10,Default,,0,0,0,,收好这个袋子\NStow the bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.50,0:37:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,-你疯了吗？-我决不能跟丢他\N- Are you nuts?- I'm not going to lose him now.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:35.78,0:37:38.83,Default,,0,0,0,,你不能尾随他们的跳跃轨道\NYou can't just piggyback their jump!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.83,0:37:49.55,Default,,0,0,0,,牵引光速！你疯了吗？我们会被扯碎的···\NA tractor beam! Are you insane?We're going to rip to...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.90,0:38:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,-那是什么东西？-看来我们来了不速之客\N- What the hell is that?- We've got company.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:18.20,0:38:21.03,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，不速之客？你什么意思？\NExcuse me, company？What do you mean company
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.20,0:38:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,看到这个信号了吗？看来有人搭上了我们的跳跃轨道便车\NSee that blip? It's like somebody hitched onto our jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.50,0:38:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,这会改变我们的航线，我要他们死！就是现在！宰了他们！\NThat could change our trajectory.I want them dead! Now! Take 'em down!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.25,0:38:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我从来没有听说过有人能够在超空间进行攻击\NBut I've never heard of anyone firing on a ship in hyperspace.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:32.46,0:38:35.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你还有其他好主意吗？马上照我说的做！\NDo you have a better idea? Do it! Now!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:35.55,0:38:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,伙计，这是在自杀\NMan, that's suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:47.69,0:38:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,-他们完全失去信号了，无人机毁了 -派轰炸机去\N- We lost them all. They're toast.- Send the bomber.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:52.57,0:38:55.69,Default,,0,0,0,,再多说一句话，我就送你去\NOne more word, and I'll send you.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.79,0:39:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,我们被击中了！我就知道！\NWe're hit! I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:07.58,0:39:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,都怪你！\NThis is all your fault!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:15.71,0:39:17.34,Default,,0,0,0,,赶紧做点什么！\NDo something!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:31.02,0:39:32.77,Default,,0,0,0,,通道马上要崩溃了\NThe tunnel's breaking up!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.23,0:39:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们不可能成功的！\NWe're not going to make it!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.29,0:39:48.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好！来吧！\NYes! Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.78,0:40:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我感应到那把钥匙就在附近\NI sense the key is here.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.03,0:40:28.33,Default,,0,0,0,,现在，最好由我和齐克先独自弄明白威胁的情况\NFor the moment, it is best if Zeek and I assess the threat alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:56.54,0:41:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,我的药\NMy ampoules.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.72,0:42:07.39,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕要轮到你了\NI'm afraid it's down to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:08.26,0:42:10.47,Default,,0,0,0,,不要，求求你\NNo. Please.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:18.69,0:42:20.48,Default,,0,0,0,,兰伯特，报告损害程度\NLambert, damage report.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:22.78,0:42:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我要损害程度报告\NI want a damage report!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.91,0:42:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,别担心，我没事\NDon't worry, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:38.08,0:42:40.29,Default,,0,0,0,,是么？你以为我关心这个吗？\NYeah? Like I give a shit!
Dialogue: 0,0:42:40.75,0:42:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们的武器储备还有多少？\NWhat's the status on the double D-40s and munitions?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:44.38,0:42:45.92,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都在\NWe found a wheel.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:46.05,0:42:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,人员状况？\NPersonnel?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:48.93,0:42:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,有78%死亡或失踪\NSeventy-eight percent dead or missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:51.35,0:42:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,生命迹象扫描呢？\NLife-scan?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:54.93,0:42:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这里有小镇，好像在北方10-12英里远处\NThere's a town, looks like it's about 10 or 12 miles north of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:59.56,0:43:00.90,Default,,0,0,0,,飞行状态？\NFlight status?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:01.48,0:43:03.28,Default,,0,0,0,,你是在开玩笑吧！\NYou've got to be kidding.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:03.40,0:43:06.03,Default,,0,0,0,,拿起武器，让那些殿后的人···\NGather the weapons,what's left of my men...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:06.07,0:43:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,杀掉那些受伤无法战斗的，我们马上出发\Nshoot the injured. We're moving on.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:37.77,0:43:40.02,Default,,0,0,0,,现在还觉得爽吗？\NWas it good for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:43:43.36,0:43:45.32,Default,,0,0,0,,从现在开始我要对你这样做\NI'll start you off like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:45.36,0:43:49.70,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来的三四天里，我得依靠你来制造药剂了\NThe next step, in three or four days,depending on your production...
Dialogue: 0,0:43:49.78,0:43:52.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你就像一个药物合成储罐一样\Nwill be the body tank.
Dialogue: 0,0:43:54.62,0:43:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,你丫疯子\NYou're sick!
Dialogue: 0,0:43:56.95,0:43:59.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我是个疯狂的天才\NI'm a sick genius.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:52.00,0:44:53.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我不能呼吸了\NI can't breathe.
Dialogue: 0,0:44:54.51,0:44:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,离我远点！\NGet off my face!
Dialogue: 0,0:44:59.55,0:45:00.93,Default,,0,0,0,,你是什么东西？\NWhat are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:00.97,0:45:03.43,Default,,0,0,0,,我是齐克，你是谁？\NI'm Zeek, what are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:07.60,0:45:09.27,Default,,0,0,0,,你的身体真是柔软\NYou're so soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:10.06,0:45:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我比你想象中的要强，石头人\NI'm harder than you think, stone man.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.23,0:45:16.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你绝对不能碰我的主人奥丁的所有物\NPlease, you must not touch my master Odin's property.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.28,0:45:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,他命我来看守这个\NHe's left me with the responsibility to guard it.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.70,0:45:23.79,Default,,0,0,0,,轻松点，我对你看守的东西没兴趣，你的主人在哪里？\NRelax, your thing is safe with me.Where is your master?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:23.87,0:45:25.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我就是奥丁\NI am Odin.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.54,0:45:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,请原谅我的小兄弟，他对于自己的职责非常认真\NPlease excuse my little friend,he takes his duties very seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.13,0:45:33.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-你的名字是？-FAKK 朱莉\N- What are you called?- FAKK Julie.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:35.13,0:45:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉，好柔软，非常柔软\NJulie, soft. Very soft.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:39.84,0:45:42.10,Default,,0,0,0,,你并不是我们这个世界的人吧？\NYou're not from our world, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.35,0:45:44.68,Default,,0,0,0,,不清楚，这是哪里？\NHardly. What is this place?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.14,0:45:49.23,Default,,0,0,0,,乌诺波诺斯，有人称这里家，也有人说这里是地狱\NUroboris. Some call it home.Others call it hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:49.56,0:45:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我的主人说你们从天上来\NMy master says you come from the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.15,0:45:54.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你手上有那东西吗？你有那把钥匙吗？\NDo you have it? Do you have the key?
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.36,0:45:57.49,Default,,0,0,0,,我不知道什么钥匙？\NI don't know anything about a key.
Dialogue: 0,0:45:57.53,0:46:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,我追到这里来是为了杀掉一个疯子，他能够死而复生\NI crashed here trying to kill a madman,who won't die.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:00.36,0:46:02.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我确实看到两个火球\NI did see two fireballs.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:02.83,0:46:06.58,Default,,0,0,0,,另一个火球坠落到山塔尔城市方向\NThe other was headed in the direction of a city called Shantaar.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:07.50,0:46:10.33,Default,,0,0,0,,离这里不远，我们带你过去\NIt's not far from here. We'll take you there.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:11.42,0:46:13.71,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯嗯，和我们一起走吧\NSo please, come with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.67,0:46:17.42,Default,,0,0,0,,和我讲讲那个疯子的事情\NTell me more about this madman.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:18.42,0:46:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,他叫泰勒，他将我所有关心的人都杀掉了\NBastard named Tyler,killed everyone I ever cared about.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:22.47,0:46:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,我们的传说里提到拥有钥匙的人都会变得疯狂\NOur legends say that whoever carries the key, becomes insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:28.31,0:46:30.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那肯定就是他\NThat's him all right.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.06,0:46:34.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我很抱歉，我能感觉到你的悲伤\NI'm sorry. I sense your sadness.
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.32,0:46:38.03,Default,,0,0,0,,你的族群只剩下你一个人一定非常难受\NIt's hard to be the last of your people.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:46.05,0:47:49.01,Default,,0,0,0,,没几个像样的，不过总算是个开始\NNot much of an army. But it's a start.
Dialogue: 0,0:47:49.81,0:47:53.64,Default,,0,0,0,,看，最丑的那个家伙好像坐在我的位子上\NLook. The ugliest one seems to be sitting in my chair.
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.21,0:48:21.80,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，最丑的家伙\NHey, you, ugly!
Dialogue: 0,0:48:23.26,0:48:26.39,Default,,0,0,0,,你的母亲是下贱的赫克特人\NYour mother is a Hectarian whore's handbag!
Dialogue: 0,0:49:01.50,0:49:05.09,Default,,0,0,0,,熔岩？我们要跨过这个吗？\NMolten lava? We have to cross this?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:05.34,0:49:08.68,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，山塔特 在另一边\NYes, Shantaar lies on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:10.39,0:49:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,-我讨厌这地方 -我们怎么过去？\N- I hate this place.- How are we going to cross?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:16.73,0:49:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我是查拖格，红河的守护者\NI am Chartog, guardian of the Red River.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:22.19,0:49:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道怎么过去\NI know the way across...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:25.07,0:49:27.11,Default,,0,0,0,,我会告诉你\Nand I will tell you.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:28.66,0:49:30.49,Default,,0,0,0,,你只需要\NYou just have to...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:31.91,0:49:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我一下\Nkiss me.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:34.12,0:49:35.29,Default,,0,0,0,,没门\NNo way.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.41,0:49:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么呐？宝贝\NWhat's the matter, my precious?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:40.71,0:49:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你没发现我的巨大魅力吗？\NDon't you find me attractive?
Dialogue: 0,0:49:46.01,0:49:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这是杀掉泰勒所必须付出的代价的话···\NIf this is what it takes to kill Tyler....
Dialogue: 0,0:49:50.18,0:49:53.85,Default,,0,0,0,,这才像话，帮帮你的朋友\NThat's a good girl. Help your friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:54.35,0:49:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,很快的\NIt will be over soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:49:57.56,0:50:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,那我返回得亲谁？\NWho will I have to kiss to get back?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.24,0:50:12.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你在干嘛？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.03,0:50:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,我们都在等你\NWe're waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:17.29,0:50:20.46,Default,,0,0,0,,混蛋，亲这个去吧！\NSon of a bitch! Kiss this!
Dialogue: 0,0:50:24.96,0:50:27.59,Default,,0,0,0,,你们这些人的风俗真奇怪\NYour people have strange customs.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.84,0:50:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,随你怎么说\NTell me about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.45,0:51:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,像是死亡呀，永生什么的\NMortality sucks, immortality sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:00.66,0:51:02.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所有这些鬼东西\NEverything sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:05.42,0:51:06.59,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，见鬼\NOh, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:09.09,0:51:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,这真是搓\NThis really sucks.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:46.21,0:51:48.17,Default,,0,0,0,,那家伙是你寻找的人吗？\NIs he the one you search for?
Dialogue: 0,0:51:49.67,0:51:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,哦，是的\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:51:58.47,0:52:00.43,Default,,0,0,0,,哈！上呀，泰勒！\NYeah! Come on, Tyler!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:15.78,0:52:18.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我是你的新头头！是我\NI'm your new leader! Me!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.08,0:52:28.00,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我们惨了\NNow we're up the creek.
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.06,0:52:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,当你杀掉某人时\NWhen you kill someone...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:44.60,0:52:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,确保他已经死透了\Nmake sure they're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.07,0:52:55.32,Default,,0,0,0,,哟，宝贝\NYo, baby.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:07.00,0:53:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我是泰勒!你的新主人！\NI am Tyler! Your new lord!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:24.27,0:53:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,盲目的欢呼声真令人陶醉\NBlind adulation makes me so horny.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:28.77,0:53:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,给我个女人\NBring me a wench!
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.03,0:53:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,主人，他就是那个持有钥匙的人，不是吗？\NMaster, he's the one with the key, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:53:43.20,0:53:46.16,Default,,0,0,0,,恐怕就凭我们的力量对付不了他\NHe's far too powerful for us to deal with alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:46.20,0:53:47.66,Default,,0,0,0,,让我来\NLeave that to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:47.83,0:53:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉，你太冲动了，三思而行呐\NJulie, you are too impulsive.Please, think about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:52.79,0:53:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,-考虑什么东西？-那把钥匙\N- Think about what?- The key.
Dialogue: 0,0:53:56.42,0:53:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不明白 -你担心的是那把钥匙\N- You don't understand.- You worry about the key.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:00.09,0:54:01.76,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒是我的\NTyler's mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:04.89,0:54:08.56,Default,,0,0,0,,她心里只剩下对复仇的渴望\NShe is letting her thirst for revenge rule her mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:54:38.22,0:54:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,一个新造型，但是··\NA little retro, but hey....
Dialogue: 0,0:54:51.10,0:54:52.85,Default,,0,0,0,,他们在哪里发现你的？\NWhere'd they find you?
Dialogue: 0,0:54:54.15,0:54:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说你很特别，所以不辞万里来见你\NI hear you're very special.I've come a long way to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.16,0:55:08.04,Default,,0,0,0,,-你不是机器人吧？-为什么你不自己来试试？\N- You're not a robot, are you?- Why don't you find out for yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:08.87,0:55:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我想我死了 并且去了天堂\NI could say I've died and gone to heaven, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:12.58,0:55:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,那不可能\Nthat wouldn't be true.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:14.71,0:55:18.55,Default,,0,0,0,,哪部分？死掉抑或是去天堂？\NWhich part, the dying or the heaven?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:21.63,0:55:22.63,Default,,0,0,0,,你\NYou.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:27.81,0:55:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道我的魅力无人可挡，你到底想要什么呢？\NI know I'm irresistible,but what do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:31.39,0:55:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我要你\NI want you...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:34.10,0:55:36.15,Default,,0,0,0,,还有你拥有的一切\Nand what you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:36.31,0:55:39.19,Default,,0,0,0,,我拥有获得永生的钥匙\NThere's a price to pay for immortality...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:39.32,0:55:42.20,Default,,0,0,0,,宇宙也即将付出迎来变革\Nand the universe is going to pick up the tab.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:43.45,0:55:44.95,Default,,0,0,0,,多么具有独创性\NHow original.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:45.53,0:55:47.83,Default,,0,0,0,,每个国王都必须有一个皇后\NEvery king must have a queen.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:49.37,0:55:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,你想要我？\NDo you want me?
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.83,0:55:53.58,Default,,0,0,0,,你不妨大胆猜一猜\NTake a wild guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:55:58.46,0:55:59.67,Default,,0,0,0,,永远？\NForever?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:00.59,0:56:01.80,Default,,0,0,0,,闭嘴\NShut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:56:12.93,0:56:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这次不行\NNot this time!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:16.90,0:56:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,贱人！\NBitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:18.23,0:56:20.19,Default,,0,0,0,,去死吧！\NTime to die!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:25.95,0:56:26.95,Default,,0,0,0,,死吧！\NDie!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:32.91,0:56:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,你在做什么？\NWhat are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:35.67,0:56:39.63,Default,,0,0,0,,-停下！-我做不到！这是主人命令！\N- Stop!- I can't! The master told me!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:42.76,0:56:44.26,Default,,0,0,0,,你这个蠢石头！\NYou stupid rock!
Dialogue: 0,0:56:54.85,0:56:57.98,Default,,0,0,0,,我怎么可能会死在这里？\NWhat does it take to get laid around here?
Dialogue: 0,0:56:58.65,0:57:02.53,Default,,0,0,0,,我抓到他了，就在刚才，我明明马上就能杀掉他的\NI had him! Ten more seconds,and he was dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.15,0:57:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我们认为你陷入困境了\NWe thought you were in trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:05.57,0:57:08.45,Default,,0,0,0,,朱莉，太晚了\NJulie, it's too late.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:09.03,0:57:11.58,Default,,0,0,0,,这已经不再仅仅是你和泰勒之间的事情了\NIt's not just about you and Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:12.41,0:57:16.29,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒寻找的东西就藏在圣域\NWhat Tyler seeks lies within the walls of the Holylands.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:17.29,0:57:21.55,Default,,0,0,0,,他会到来并审判我们\NHe will come and we will all be judged.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:23.13,0:57:25.97,Default,,0,0,0,,你说你没找到他们是什么意思？\NWhat do you mean you can't find them?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.76,0:57:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你居然会跟丢一个6尺女人和一块会说话的石头？\NHow do you lose a 6-foot bitch with a talking rock?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:33.22,0:57:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们是干嘛吃的？\NHow do you do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:34.85,0:57:38.40,Default,,0,0,0,,-我们到处都找遍了  -你们这帮蠢货！\N- We looked everywhere.- You idiots!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:38.69,0:57:39.86,Default,,0,0,0,,集合部队！\NGather the troops!
Dialogue: 0,0:57:41.52,0:57:43.15,Default,,0,0,0,,这就是？\NThis is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:57:44.69,0:57:48.78,Default,,0,0,0,,我相信得用点酒水和社会交际技巧来融入你们\NI sure could use a drink and a little social give and take.
Dialogue: 0,0:57:51.28,0:57:53.20,Default,,0,0,0,,主意不错\NThere goes that idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:09.68,0:58:14.06,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能休息一会？我年纪有点大了\NCan we stop for a moment?I'm not as young as I once was.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:14.51,0:58:16.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我来查看周围的状况\NI'll see what lies beyond.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:20.65,0:58:22.52,Default,,0,0,0,,伊甸很美丽！\NEden was beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:23.11,0:58:25.07,Default,,0,0,0,,可是被他毁掉了\NThen he destroyed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:25.40,0:58:27.86,Default,,0,0,0,,主人，你过来看看\NMaster, come see!
Dialogue: 0,0:58:53.51,0:58:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,是时候进行下一阶段了\NIt's time for the next phase.
Dialogue: 0,0:58:59.52,0:59:00.52,Default,,0,0,0,,求求你\NPlease.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:00.85,0:59:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,五分钟内，你将失去所有感觉\NIn five minutes, you will lose all senses.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:07.15,0:59:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你就好像安静地死去了一样\NIt will seem like a very peaceful dying.
Dialogue: 0,0:59:10.78,0:59:13.57,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？我们来了不速之客\NWhat? We have company.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:03.54,1:00:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢这样吗？\NDo you like this?
Dialogue: 0,1:00:14.26,1:00:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你不应该那样做的\NYou shouldn't have done that.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:32.99,1:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我很伤心\NNow I'm really upset!
Dialogue: 0,1:00:39.78,1:00:43.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我很担心，主人， 朱莉进去有好一会了\NI am worried, Master.The soft one has been inside too long.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.87,1:00:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿，小家伙\NHere, kitty.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:49.75,1:00:51.80,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道你在哪儿\NI know where you are.
Dialogue: 0,1:00:51.84,1:00:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,我能闻到你\NI can smell you.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:01.31,1:01:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,救命！\NHelp me!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:07.73,1:01:11.19,Default,,0,0,0,,-凯瑞，其他人呢？-他们都死了\N- Kerrie, what about the others?- They're all dead.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:13.19,1:01:14.49,Default,,0,0,0,,抓住我\NHang on to me.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:20.16,1:01:21.28,Default,,0,0,0,,没事\NIt's okay.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:23.12,1:01:24.37,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这附近\NNearly there.
Dialogue: 0,1:01:30.09,1:01:31.29,Default,,0,0,0,,快跑！\NHurry, run!
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.82,1:01:58.78,Default,,0,0,0,,那不是我们坠毁的地方吗？\NIsn't that where we crashed?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:01.16,1:02:02.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我的药剂！\NMy ampoules!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:13.13,1:02:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,我会带上这把斧头然后找到那个贱人\NI've had it up to here with that bitch!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:16.30,1:02:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,当我找到她，我会让她不朽，这样我就可以不断折磨她，杀死她\NWhen I find her, I'll make her immortal so I can screw her and kill her
Dialogue: 0,1:02:21.51,1:02:25.47,Default,,0,0,0,,每天，每个小时，来娱乐自己！\Nevery hour of every day for all eternity!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:25.77,1:02:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我们现在向圣域前进\NWe march on the Holyland now!
Dialogue: 0,1:02:36.11,1:02:38.99,Default,,0,0,0,,钥匙所到之处，恐惧如影随形\NWhere the key goes, horror follows.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:39.03,1:02:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,一切都将臣服于永生之下\NAll in the sacred name of immortality.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:42.87,1:02:43.99,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么是我们？\NWhy us?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:44.12,1:02:47.45,Default,,0,0,0,,难道你们那本古书没教你们关于阿肯人的事情？\NDo your ancient books not teach you about the Arakacians?
Dialogue: 0,1:02:47.54,1:02:49.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我们没有古书\NWe have no ancient books.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:49.58,1:02:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯人被毁灭了，因此我们才能生活在和平中\NThey were destroyed so our people could live in peace...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:52.42,1:02:54.67,Default,,0,0,0,,同时也失去了关于过去那些邪恶之事的记忆\Nwithout the memory of past evil.
Dialogue: 0,1:02:55.84,1:02:59.72,Default,,0,0,0,,忘记历史只会令邪恶东山再起，朱莉\NTo forget history is to allow evil to rise again, Julie.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.22,1:03:02.59,Default,,0,0,0,,然后到来更多的罪恶和混乱\NMore sinister and ruthless than ever.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:02.68,1:03:06.06,Default,,0,0,0,,-泰勒是阿肯人吗？    -他不是\N- Is Tyler an Arakacian?- He is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:06.26,1:03:10.56,Default,,0,0,0,,很多实际以前，阿肯人发现了古神之泪\NMany centuries ago, the Arakacians discovered an ancient tear...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:10.73,1:03:14.27,Default,,0,0,0,,在宇宙形成过程中所产生的所有造物之中\Nin the fabric of the universe from which flowed a liquid...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:14.31,1:03:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,它能够赐予永生\Ncapable of bestowing immortality.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:17.11,1:03:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,他们奴役我的祖先强迫他们制造一个密室\NThey enslaved my ancestors and forced them to build a chamber...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:21.49,1:03:25.16,Default,,0,0,0,,密室就在应许之地用来收藏那古神之泪\Nin the Holylands to contain this unnatural power.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:26.12,1:03:29.50,Default,,0,0,0,,因此阿肯人才能实行残暴地统治，直到\NAnd so it was that the Arakacians ruled in infamy until...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:29.54,1:03:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我的祖先锁住密室并将钥匙流放到宇宙深处\Nmy people were able to lock the chamber and cast the key deep into space.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.42,1:03:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,没有赐予永生的古神之泪，阿肯人变得普通\NWithout their life-giving waters,the Arakacians became mortal...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.59,1:03:43.26,Default,,0,0,0,,我们最终打败他们\Nand we were finally able to defeat them.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.97,1:03:45.93,Default,,0,0,0,,但是现在泰勒拥有钥匙\NBut now Tyler has the key.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.01,1:03:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,是的，那把钥匙能够带来永生的可能\NYes. The key which holds the promise of immortality...
Dialogue: 0,1:03:49.56,1:03:52.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是也会令他发疯\Nbut also renders its bearer insane.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:53.19,1:03:54.94,Default,,0,0,0,,就像诅咒一样\NSuch is the curse.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:56.02,1:03:59.11,Default,,0,0,0,,可能永生？但他已经不可战胜了\NThe promise of immortality?He's already invincible.
Dialogue: 0,1:03:59.15,1:04:01.36,Default,,0,0,0,,不，他还不是\NNo. He is not.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:02.70,1:04:05.91,Default,,0,0,0,,那把钥匙将会指引他找到古神之泪\NThe key is guiding him to the everlasting waters...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:05.99,1:04:07.87,Default,,0,0,0,,但是他还没有得到它\Nbut he has yet to reach them.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:07.91,1:04:10.08,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么他要摧毁伊甸？\NWhy did he have to destroy Eden?
Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.25,1:04:13.29,Default,,0,0,0,,阿肯人也曾经占领你们故乡\NThe Arakacians also occupied your colony...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.62,1:04:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,如同他们蹂躏宇宙其他地方时一样，他们在伊甸储藏了一些古神之泪\Nand stored some of the liquid there as they ravaged the universe.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.04,1:04:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这么多年过去，古神之泪遍布伊甸\NOver time it seeped into the earth.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:20.46,1:04:23.80,Default,,0,0,0,,你的族人逐渐将它吸入自己的身体中\NYour people absorbed traces of it into their systems.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.05,1:04:26.59,Default,,0,0,0,,泰勒便从他们的身体中提取药剂\NWhich Tyler distilled from their bodies!
Dialogue: 0,1:04:28.01,1:04:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,但这并不以令他不朽\NNot enough to render him immortal...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:30.43,1:04:33.39,Default,,0,0,0,,可也足够他得到力量到达密室\Nbut now he has the strength to reach the chamber.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:33.43,1:04:37.11,Default,,0,0,0,,就因为他对力量的渴望便毁灭了我的族群\NA whole people destroyed because of the lust for power of one man.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:37.52,1:04:41.57,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事在以前也发生过，朱莉，并且以后也会重演\NIt has happened before, Julie.It will happen again.
Dialogue: 0,1:04:42.74,1:04:44.11,Default,,0,0,0,,但绝不会是泰勒\NNot with Tyler.
Dialogue: 0,1:05:39.13,1:05:41.34,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回来，奥丁长老\NWelcome back, Master Odin!
Dialogue: 0,1:05:56.48,1:06:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,-奥丁，那把钥匙是不是已经来到这里了？-恐怕是的\N- Odin, the key? ls it here?- I'm afraid so.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:00.77,1:06:02.61,Default,,0,0,0,,如同我们所说，运输队伍\NAs we speak, the carrier...
Dialogue: 0,1:06:02.65,1:06:06.49,Default,,0,0,0,,还有山塔特的渣滓们正在向我们的城市而来\Nand the vile scum of Shantaar descend upon our city.
Dialogue: 0,1:06:07.36,1:06:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须尽我们所能做好准备，我们要战斗直到死亡\NWe have done all we can to prepare.We will fight to the death.
Dialogue: 0,1:07:58.10,1:07:59.77,Default,,0,0,0,,你们认识？\NYou know each other?
Dialogue: 0,1:07:59.93,1:08:02.10,Default,,0,0,0,,他在学校时打算救我\NHe tried to save me at the school.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:02.60,1:08:04.02,Default,,0,0,0,,那没什么\NIt was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:05.40,1:08:07.15,Default,,0,0,0,,你们在哪里认识的？\NAnd where did you meet?
Dialogue: 0,1:08:07.77,1:08:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是姐妹\NWe're sisters.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:10.28,1:08:11.49,Default,,0,0,0,,姐妹？！\NSisters!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.70,1:08:15.62,Default,,0,0,0,,长老都被杀掉了，我们中一定有叛徒！\NThe elders have been killed!There's a traitor among us!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.66,1:08:17.03,Default,,0,0,0,,警告其他人\NWarn the others!
Dialogue: 0,1:08:19.54,1:08:20.75,Default,,0,0,0,,就在这里\NThere it is.
Dialogue: 0,1:08:21.95,1:08:25.71,Default,,0,0,0,,永生的密室，里面就是古神之泪\NThe Chamber of lmmortality,that holds the everlasting waters.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.54,1:09:06.83,Default,,0,0,0,,最后一个\NThe last one.
Dialogue: 0,1:09:34.86,1:09:37.45,Default,,0,0,0,,大家准备战斗！上！\NEverybody fight! Come on!
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.83,1:10:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越糟了\NThis is going to suck!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:43.41,1:11:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,傻瓜！\NYou fool!
Dialogue: 0,1:11:45.20,1:11:47.37,Default,,0,0,0,,那是我最后一个了\NThat was my last one!
Dialogue: 0,1:12:41.88,1:12:44.80,Default,,0,0,0,,-谢谢你，软家伙   -不用谢\N- Thank you, soft one.- Anytime.
Dialogue: 0,1:13:03.19,1:13:04.45,Default,,0,0,0,,喂，混蛋！\NHey, asshole!
Dialogue: 0,1:13:06.03,1:13:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,又是你！\NYou again!
Dialogue: 0,1:14:04.55,1:14:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,你想我了吗？\NDid you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:21.98,1:14:24.44,Default,,0,0,0,,你总是伤害你爱的人\NYou always hurt the ones you love.
Dialogue: 0,1:14:24.78,1:14:26.11,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样吗？\NLike this?
Dialogue: 0,1:14:36.45,1:14:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,保持这样子，我马上回来\NHold that pose. I'll be right back.
Dialogue: 0,1:15:07.48,1:15:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我的，全都是我的！\NIt's mine. It's all mine!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:31.26,1:15:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,来吧，贱人！你真的惹火我了！\NBring it on, bitch!You're really starting to piss me off!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:35.60,1:15:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,你没资格拿到圣水\NYou are not worthy of the Holy Waters!
Dialogue: 0,1:15:40.52,1:15:41.69,Default,,0,0,0,,至少今天不行\NNot today.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:07.46,1:16:10.30,Default,,0,0,0,,记住今天是你的忌日\NRemember this on your way to hell!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:13.30,1:16:14.68,Default,,0,0,0,,FAKK 2!\NFAKK 2!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:16.60,1:16:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,这疯狂的事情马上就要结束了\NThe insanity has to end now.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:26.36,1:16:28.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我们必须毁掉那把钥匙\NWe must destroy the key.
Dialogue: 0,1:16:30.32,1:16:31.82,Default,,0,0,0,,或者不用\NPerhaps not!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:36.91,1:16:37.95,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,1:16:39.08,1:16:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我是阿肯人\NBecause I am Arakacian!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:44.08,1:16:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,我的演技骗过了那些令人恶心的圣域人\NMy charade fooled the insufferable Holylanders!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:47.67,1:16:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,还有那个愚蠢的石头\NAnd even that little stone idiot!
Dialogue: 0,1:16:49.71,1:16:52.84,Default,,0,0,0,,你难道真的认为一个普通人能够阻止我？\NWhat makes you think a pathetic mortal could stop me?
Dialogue: 0,1:17:28.08,1:17:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,你个蠢货！\NYou fools!
Dialogue: 0,1:17:54.40,1:17:56.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我必须完成我的使命\NI must fulfil my destiny.
Dialogue: 0,1:18:19.22,1:18:22.30,Default,,0,0,0,,-你应该如此  -齐克，我命令你！\N- You must!- Zeek, I command you!
Dialogue: 0,1:18:32.19,1:18:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,再见，软家伙，我永远不会忘记你\NGood-bye, soft one. I'll never forget you.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:10.64,1:19:11.77,Default,,0,0,0,,结束了\NIt's over.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:17.86,1:19:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,-让我来帮你    -哦，不会吧，他还活着\N- Let me help you.- Oh, no. He survived.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:21.82,1:19:23.07,Default,,0,0,0,,你还好吗？\NAre you okay?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:23.70,1:19:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,你看我怎么样，你这个白痴？\NWhat does it look like, you dickhead?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:35.21,1:19:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,永恒意味着长久的孤独\NEternity is a long time to spend alone.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:39.51,1:19:41.38,Default,,0,0,0,,你在说什么？\NWhat are you talking about?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:42.84,1:19:45.60,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是意味着我们要变得不朽？\NDoes this mean we're all going to be immortal?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:46.56,1:19:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,因为如果这是真的，你知道···\N'Cause if that's true, you know....
Dialogue: 0,1:19:48.52,1:19:51.31,Default,,0,0,0,,听我说，我要去四处转转很长一段时间\NListen, I'm going to be around for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,1:19:51.98,1:19:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,谁拿着钥匙？\NWho took the key?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:53.90,1:19:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,这是不是意味着我们现在是朋友？\NDoes this mean we're friends now?
Dialogue: 0,1:19:55.86,1:19:58.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我给你添了不少麻烦，所以···\N'Cause I've been putting up with a lot of your crap, so...
Dialogue: 0,1:19:59.44,1:20:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为现在是回报的时间了，来吧，你知道你是爱我的\Nl think it's payback time.Come on, you know you love me.
Dialogue: 0,1:20:22.59,1:20:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,就这样，那把通往永生密室的钥匙\NAnd so the key to the chamber of immortality...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:27.14,1:20:32.23,Default,,0,0,0,,再次被流放到宇宙沉寂的深处\Nwas once again cast out into the silent gulfs of space...
Dialogue: 0,1:20:33.85,1:20:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,一个新的石像守护者看守着它对抗邪恶\Nwith a new stone protector to guard it against evil.

